<page title="Installing Closure HTML">

  <h3>Download</h3>
  <p>
    <strike>
    Download a
    <a href="http://common-lisp.net/project/closure/download/">tarball</a>.</strike>
    (Not available yet.)
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="http://repo.or.cz/w/closure-html.git">
      Get it from repo.or.cz using git.
    </a>
  </p>

  <h3>Installation</h3>
  <p>
    Closure HTML needs
    <a href="http://www.cliki.net/closure-common">closure-common</a>
    from cxml CVS and <a href="http://weitz.de/flexi-streams/">flexi-streams</a>.
    <a href="http://www.cliki.net/asdf">ASDF</a> is used for
    compilation.  Register the .asd file, e.g. by symlinking it, then
    compile cxml-stp using <tt>asdf:operate</tt>.
  </p>
  <pre>$ ln -sf `pwd`/closure-html.asd /path/to/your/registry/
* (asdf:operate 'asdf:load-op :closure-html)</pre>

</page>
